  "texts": [
    "Construct dataset of masked sentences S:",
    "For every mention of x ∈ X in T, we extract the surrounding sentence, and mask the mention of x (replacing x with a special [MASK] token) in the sentence.",
    "Compute A for each sentence: For each sentence s x ∈ S where x is the masked entity, we compute the probability, according to an MLM, that the [MASK] would be replaced with either human pronouns (e.g., \"he\", \"she\") or non-human pronouns (e.g., \"it\"), i.e., P HUMAN (s x) = w∈human pronouns P (w),",
    "w∈non-human pronouns P (w),",
    "where P (w) is the model's outputted probability of replacing the mask with the word w. (See Appendix B.1 for the full list of human and non-human pronouns.)"
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}